<item>
            <title>[LOG4J2-3587] Cannot create Rfc5424Layout without enterpriseNumber after upgrading to 2.18.0</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-3587</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I get an exception when using&#160;&lt;tt&gt;Rfc5424Layout&lt;/tt&gt; after upgrading to 2.18.0 (but it works in 2.17.2). Using this configuration:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&amp;lt;Configuration&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;Appenders&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;Console name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;stdout&quot;&lt;/span&gt; target=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;SYSTEM_OUT&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;Rfc5424Layout /&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;/Console&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;/Appenders&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/Configuration&amp;gt; &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I get this when starting my application:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: No enterprise number was supplied
	at org.apache.logging.log4j.message.StructuredDataId.&amp;lt;init&amp;gt;(StructuredDataId.java:169)
	at org.apache.logging.log4j.message.StructuredDataId.&amp;lt;init&amp;gt;(StructuredDataId.java:132)
	at org.apache.logging.log4j.core.layout.Rfc5424Layout.&amp;lt;init&amp;gt;(Rfc5424Layout.java:149)
	at org.apache.logging.log4j.core.layout.Rfc5424Layout.createLayout(Rfc5424Layout.java:643) &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I need to specify an enterpriseNumber for Rfc5424Layout like this to make it work:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&amp;lt;Configuration&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;Appenders&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;Console name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;stdout&quot;&lt;/span&gt; target=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;SYSTEM_OUT&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;Rfc5424Layout enterpriseNumber=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;123456&quot;&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;/Console&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;/Appenders&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/Configuration&amp;gt; &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
